    "body": "The way I got around this was just `ignore`ing the bindings path in `rustfmt.toml` and using `cargo +nightly fmt --check` in CI. It's arguably reasonable to not format generated code, so, definitely understand just closing this as won't fix.\r\n\r\nIf desirable I can open an issue or PR on the template repo with a `rustfmt.toml` and update the action to use nightly fmt. Let me know if that would be useful.",
